{"tid":2258583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港人李彬豪慘被台灣驅逐出境","createTime":"2020-10-26T06:53:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T10:10:43.000Z","uid":313615,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"bbb049fd6c80dafc79dce66cedc9d2fc45d48c9d","tid":2258583,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:53:17.000Z","msg":"前「學生動源」召集人鍾翰林、洪英棠與洪心弦去年1月赴台灣，與《自由時報》政治組副主任蘇永耀、台灣青年反共救國團理事長楊月清見面，卻被偷拍放上香港《文匯報》、《大公報》頭版稱兩人暗會總統蔡英文「密使」<br />\n<br />\n台灣移民署10月25日表示，香港人李彬豪喺台灣從事跟蹤拍攝港青訪問活動，廢止佢在台居留許可，並強制驅逐出境，且管制一定期間不得赴台。<br />\n<br />\n李已遭任職的科技公司解僱，原在台的居留身份亦已遭移除。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201025/Z2LCO37APZFSZHGK25TEMFRBD4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201025%2FZ2LCO37APZFSZHGK25TEMFRBD4%2F&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oMbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=32991484\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201025%2FZ2LCO37APZFSZHGK25TEMFRBD4%2F&h=cdfcdb7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201025/Z2LCO37APZFSZHGK25TEMFRBD4/</a>"},{"pid":"e21f61fcde8cd22a300bb21be94ef654cfcea204","tid":2258583,"uid":313615,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w7gcgzr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw7gcgzr.png&h=f0b4fb25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李彬豪係香港大學專業進修學院副學士，2015年赴台就讀輔大心理系，去年畢業後曾喺科技公司擔任業務工程師"},{"pid":"08799c650a278b662e829b9cfd188b7aa2fe9ce5","tid":2258583,"uid":101544,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:56:45.000Z","msg":"返黎啦孩子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c877a9578c3fdf190a6becc50657609303d00888","tid":2258583,"uid":116960,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e21f61fcde8cd22a300bb21be94ef654cfcea204","tid":2258583,"uid":313615,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:55:10.000Z","msg":"<